<article class="post">
  <div class="title" >
    <a href="/post/{{id}}" target="_blank" id="post-title">{{title}}</a>
  </div>
  <div class="post-body">
    <p>{{post_url}}</p>
  </div>
  <div class="meta">
   by {{user.username}} on {{format_date created_at}}
    |
    <a href="/post/{{id}}">{{comments.length}} comment(s)</a>
  </div>
</article>
        {{!-- When we pass the post object into the partial, 
        we don't pass the object as is but rather pass in all of the properties of that object. --}}